Shopify provides a unified platform to easily manage and connect with a global customer base. You can use Shopify&#8217;s built-in functionality to customize Canadian pricing, taxes, duties, and shipping rates to maximize cross-border sales.<\/p>\n<h1>Capitalize on Canada&#8217;s Unique Opportunities<\/h1>\n<p>Canadians have their own preferences and buying behaviors worth catering to. For example, Canada has two official languages, with French-speaking customers looking for content and customer service in French. Take time to research product categories, brand preferences, and consumer trends specific to the Canadian market. Tailoring your offerings and marketing to Canadians can unlock untapped market potential.<\/p>\n<h1>Differentiate Yourself in Canada<\/h1>\n<p>With Shopify, you can highlight your unique value proposition to stand out from local Canadian and international competitors. Leverage your core strengths, customize products for Canadians, and tailor your brand messaging. Localizing your Shopify online store for Canadian shoppers can revitalize sales by positioning your business as a differentiated brand tailored just for them.<\/p>\n<h1>Achieve Greater Economies of Scale<\/h1>\n<p>Expanding to Canada with Shopify often allows merchants to achieve greater economies of scale. Selling to more Canadian customers allows you to grow your business and optimize operations. Producing, purchasing, and shipping at larger quantities can lower your costs per unit. Marketing to Canadian customers also means your advertising spend goes further. These cost efficiencies boost profit margins and provide a path out of sales slumps.<\/p>\n<h1>BorderBuddy: Your Trusted Canadian E-commerce Partner<\/h1>\n<p>International expansion to Canada through the BorderBuddy for Shopify app offers merchants an array of benefits for overcoming sales slumps. The BorderBuddy App manages customs, duties, taxes and shipping to Canada so that both merchants and customers have 100% transparency in shipping.<\/p>\n<p>Partner with BorderBuddy and Shopify to conquer Canadian e-commerce. Reach out today or visit the Shopify App Store to begin your Canadian expansion! <a href=\"tel:866-528-1963\">Give us a call<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or go to the <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/apps.shopify.com\/canadacustomsduty\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shopify App<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> store.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Are you experiencing a sales slump in your online store? An effective strategy to overcome this is through international expansion. In particular, expanding to the Canadian market via the Shopify platform could be your solution. Canada represents a $22 billion e-commerce market growing at double digit rates annually, with millions of eager customers waiting to&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3624,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_genesis_hide_title":false,"_genesis_hide_breadcrumbs":false,"_genesis_hide_singular_image":false,"_genesis_hide_footer_widgets":false,"_genesis_custom_body_class":"","_genesis_custom_post_class":"","_genesis_layout":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v22.4 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Slumping Sales? Explore Shopify&#039;s Solution: How Expansion to Canada Can Help &#187; Blog &#187; BorderBuddy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Are you experiencing a sales slump in your online store? An effective strategy to overcome this is through international expansion. In particular,\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/blog\/slumping-sal